  <div class="max-w-4xl mx-auto mt-12 px-6">
    <div class="prose prose-stone prose-lg max-w-none mb-12">
      <h2>What is MuDG?</h2>
      <p>
        Dialectics is a method of reasoning that seeks to understand things in their movement and change. It is a way of thinking that is based on the idea that everything is interconnected and that change is constant. Dialectics is a powerful tool for understanding complex systems and for making sense of the world around us.
      </p>
      <p>
        As such MuDG (Multi-user Dialectic Graph) is a tool for thought. A multiplayer chat interface to allow the full reasoning behind an argument to be followed. Many people can think together to build out a massive knowledge graph, interacting with LLMs to integrate the knowledge into the whole.
      </p>
    </div>
  </div>
  
